Text: <c.white><c.mono_sans>They are my ships. And they go</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>ROLLO: Some may even go to him</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>This was going to be the most</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>that I would give you to him?</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>as those in whom I can trust.</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I promised him that if he went</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and who keeps his tail in his</c.mono_sans></c.white>
<c.white><c.mono_sans>how can I be of use to you?</c.mono_sans></c.white>
